			<li>
				<span class="the_question">What is the Letter of Authorization (LOA)?</span>
				<span class="the_answer">In order for The Passport &amp; Visa Company to apply for a Passport on your behalf, you must provide us with an LOA. To ensure that the document contains all necessary information, please use the template that we provide you with in the application materials.</span>
