				<span class="the_answer">An official birth certificate is required for a Passport application. If you have lost your original birth certificate, since birth certificates are held under state jurisdiction, to obtain a reissue of an official birth certificate, you must request the record from your state of birth. There are services that help expedite this process. For instance vitalcheck.com is a very good tool for assisting with birth certificate requests, no matter what state you were born in.</span>
			</li>
